title: Fucking is fun ;-)
info:
The track was made in 1994 and released in 2008 in the album: Oldschool MODe

This album contains 4-channels MOD music Yerzmyey wrote throughout years, since 1994, for Amiga 500, Atari ST and ZX Spectrum. Besides, You can find here 3 guest-songs - MODs make by Factor6, TDM and Epi; the MODs have been made for ZX Spectrum and Atari XL/XE.
